OL,6,FA man has been jailed following a road
OL,7,Fcollision on Merseyside where a 13-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy was killed.
OL,10,FHarry Kinney-Ryan had just bought
OL,11,Fsweets from a petrol station near the
OL,12,FShowcase Cinema on the East Lancs Road
OL,13,Fin Croxteth and was crossing the road
OL,14,Fon December 7 2022.
OL,16,FCraig Griffiths was was in the outside
OL,17,Flane and accelerated to try and get
OL,18,Finto the inside lane, so he could turn
OL,19,Fleft at the next junction by Stonedale
OL,20,FRetail Park.
