OL,6,FBut as he was moving across, he hit
OL,7,FHarry, who was rushed to hospital
OL,8,Fwhere he died two days later.
OL,10,FGriffiths was driving at at least
OL,11,F13mph over the speed limit. He
OL,12,Fremained at the scene, and was later
OL,13,Fcharged with causing death by careless
OL,14,Fdriving.
OL,16,FAt a court hearing in June 2024
OL,17,FGriffiths, of Frinstead Road in Norris
OL,18,FGreen, pleaded guilty, and on Friday
OL,19,F12 July was sentenced to 12 months in
OL,20,Fprison at Liverpool Crown Court.
